query:
SELECT pi.id as imageId, pi.productId, pi.url, pi.displayOrder, pi.isPrimary, p.name as productName
FROM product_images pi
JOIN products p ON pi.productId = p.id
WHERE pi.id IN (510013, 510014, 510016, 510017, 510018, 510019, 510020, 510021, 510023)
ORDER BY pi.productId, pi.displayOrder;
